responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "340E616B422F00E224D8849FB0B8CC06", "The Gaffers are a secret cult of gobbuns from far in the future where a goblin utopia reigns. They praise a god they call Volton who powers all life through eesence. Malgus the Djinn is forced to play this role and as such is their false god. The Gaffers are extremely anarchist and hope to release their false god to bring about the destruction of the world.")
